      • getAuthenticatedAccount

        public Account getAuthenticatedAccount()
                                throws BaringoApiException
        Returns the Account object for the account that's currently authenticated via OAuth2, or null if none. This is a convenience method that caches, since it seems like something that might be requested frequently.

      • setApiEndpoint

        public static void setApiEndpoint(java.lang.String url)
        Used for switching to the mashape commercial endpoint, or for mocking. NOTE that there can only be one API endpoint in the system at a time; even if you create a new client, they all still share the same URL endpoints.

        url - new endpoint
